//Write a program to convert lowercase to uppercase and vice versaâ€¦

int main()
{
    char a[20];
    int i;
    printf("\n enter string:");
    gets(a);
    for(i=0;a[i]!='\0';i++)
    {
        if(a[i]>64 && a[i]<91)
            a[i]+=32;
        else if(a[i]>96 && a[i]<123)
            a[i]-=32;
    }
    printf("\n new string:%s",a);
}


Output:
enter string: smile GARG

 new string: SMILE garg

Reference:https://funcodepro.blogspot.com/2019/01/how-to-convert-lowercase-to-uppercase.html
